| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3961 — Recovery Inhibition (BrainCipher)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8b69e900-7202-5552-9e67-5a9efd34d48e"
